b><span>), it is also divisible by (N), i.e., m =E2=89=A1 0 (mod N).</span>=
</p><p dir=3D"ltr" style=3D"text-align: start;"><span>Hence, x =E2=89=A1 x'=
 (mod N, establishing uniqueness).</span></p><h2 id=3D"necessary-condition-=
